---
Source:
  - Title: The Big Red Book
    Translator: Coleman Barks
    ISBN: 987-0-06-190583-4
Page: 409
By: Rumi
---
As you start out on the way,
the way appears.

As you cease to be,
true life begins.

As your grow smaller,
the world cannot contain you.

You will be shown a being
that has no you inside it.
